Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Severe winter weather
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407brz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 Feb 1977
Severe sub-zero storms cripple many US states. Worst winter weather since 1888. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.